{"tid":239834,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"5.5day工作真係好賤","createTime":"2017-05-12T02:52:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-12T04:40:40.000Z","uid":13518,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7e78c9437dfbd918fc0f0e456f412ac236007d1f","tid":239834,"uid":13518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T02:52:30.000Z","msg":"對於我黎講 做成日野都唔係最辛苦<br />\n最辛苦就係一朝早起身個刻<br />\n平日禮拜一至五 六點收工我都可以接受<br />\n起碼真係有時間做野 我個收獲同付出真係成正比<br />\n個0.5日我真係唔知做乜鳩<br />\n又要辛苦爬落床 返到去又要做唔到啲咩野 工作地點遠既 賺返黎都比車費扣得七七八八<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都唔知點解5.5天工作仲可以生存到而家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7538749280818efee3295d4267c191e7eaca0ec","tid":239834,"uid":32906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T02:54:02.000Z","msg":"賤過狗"},{"pid":"1221f9f2cfd90e776409c0b6257e4e14d0b113cd","tid":239834,"uid":8911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T02:57:57.000Z","msg":"老世俾壓力你而攪到每日做多一粒鐘義工變相番六日咁，係咪賤過地底泥啊"},{"pid":"3a535c537f99fa7fccd69d5e1469d2135439cb41","tid":239834,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T02:59:28.000Z","msg":"全部cut做五天工作啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b50d4e82b6f5b36e13ea0e827087ad7959b956b5","tid":239834,"uid":13518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T03:04:11.000Z","msg":"今日禮拜五 我諗到聽日仲要返0.5 day <br />\n真係有少少黯然"},{"pid":"26fadbb3659cc7425f85e6742cb67f3297f9e22b","tid":239834,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T03:05:15.000Z","msg":"6點收工仲怨咩撚嘢，皇恩浩蕩啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"db482e3f8c898c28abc8155b619ef83b6cd3c7b2","tid":239834,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c